text.tspan: Join in the Last Night of the Proms celebrations in Hyde
Park, hosted by Proms in the Park stalwart Sir Terry Wogan.
The open-air concert features a host of musical stars, includ
ing Proms in the Park favourites the BBC Concert Orchestra
under the baton of Richard Balcombe, and special guests
Pumeza Matshikiza, Rufus Wainwright and legendary Earth,
Wind & Fire. Presenter Tony Blackburn joins us again to get
this year’s party under way, introducing a range of artists,
